&#7871;u b&#7841;n l&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; ki&#7871;n th&#7913;c chuy&ecirc;n s&acirc;u trong ng&agrave;nh l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh, th&igrave; nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; b&#7841;n nghe &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&oacute; v&#7867; nh&#432; l&agrave; h&#7885; &#273;ang n&oacute;i b&#7857;ng m&#7897;t th&#7913; ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; &#273;&#7871;n t&#7915; h&agrave;nh tinh kh&aacute;c v&#7853;y. Hi&#7879;n nay, s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c cho c&aacute;c l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n web nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng &#7913;ng vi&ecirc;n, v&agrave; ph&#7843;i m&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u th&aacute;ng &ndash; kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; nhi&#7873;u n&#259;m &ndash; &#273;&#7875; leo l&ecirc;n n&#7845;c thang s&#7921; nghi&#7879;p &#273;&oacute;.</p>
<p>James Somers, m&#7897;t l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n, g&#7847;n &#273;&acirc;y &#273;&atilde; vi&#7871;t <a href="http://www.aeonmagazine.com/living-together/james-somers-web-developer-money/" target="_blank">m&#7897;t b&agrave;i blog c&oacute; n&#7897;i dung r&#7857;ng:</a></p>
<p>&ldquo;T&ocirc;i c&oacute; m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh b&#7887; ngang n&#259;m th&#7913; hai tr&#432;&#7901;ng lu&#7853;t, &#273;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u h&#7885;c l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh. Hai th&aacute;ng sau, anh ta &#273;&atilde; theo h&#7885;c t&#7841;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng d&#7841;y l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh Hacker School &#7903; New York, v&agrave; 3 th&aacute;ng sau &#273;&oacute;, anh &#273;&atilde; l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c nh&#432; m&#7897;t th&#7921;c t&#7853;p sinh t&#7841;i m&#7897;t c&ocirc;ng ty t&#432; v&#7845;n chuy&ecirc;n x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng trang web cho c&aacute;c startup. Sau m&#7897;t th&aacute;ng th&#7921;c t&#7853;p &ndash; ch&uacute;ng ta &#273;ang n&oacute;i t&#7893;ng c&#7897;ng kho&#7843;ng 6 th&aacute;ng &#7903; &#273;&acirc;y &ndash; anh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7853;n v&agrave;o m&#7897;t v&#7883; tr&iacute; c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c to&agrave;n th&#7901;i gian v&#7899;i m&#7913;c l&#432;&#417;ng $85.000 &#273;&ocirc;-la (kho&#7843;ng 1.8 t&#7927; VN&#272;/n&#259;m)&rdquo;.</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-10332" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/server_01.jpg" alt="server_01" width="474" height="316" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/server_01.jpg 474w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/server_01-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 474px) 100vw, 474px"></p>
<p>Nghe c&oacute; v&#7867; v&#7915;a d&#7877; d&agrave;ng v&agrave; h&#7845;p d&#7851;n, nh&#432;ng m&#7909;c &#273;&iacute;ch c&#7911;a Somers kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; l&ocirc;i k&eacute;o ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&aacute;c nh&#7843;y v&agrave;o l&#297;nh v&#7921;c l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh. Anh than phi&#7873;n r&#7857;ng s&#7921; m&#7845;t c&acirc;n &#273;&#7889;i trong cung v&agrave; c&#7847;u v&#7873; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng l&agrave; nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n khi&#7871;n h&#7885; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tr&#7843; l&#432;&#417;ng qu&aacute; cao so v&#7899;i c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh, khi gi&aacute; tr&#7883; trong nh&#7919;ng vi&#7879;c h&#7885; l&agrave;m l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng l&#7899;n l&#7855;m so v&#7899;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c kh&aacute;c, v&iacute; d&#7909; cu&#7897;c chi&#7871;n ch&#7889;ng l&#7841;i d&#7883;ch b&#7879;nh HIV-AIDS &#7903; ch&acirc;u Phi. &#272;&oacute; l&agrave; m&#7897;t l&#7901;i ch&#7881; tr&iacute;ch c&ocirc;ng b&#7857;ng, nh&#432;ng &#7849;n trong s&#7921; v&#7905; m&#7897;ng &#273;&oacute; c&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; th&#7853;t: C&oacute; nh&#7919;ng c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c c&oacute; s&#7861;n ngo&agrave;i kia v&agrave; c&oacute; nh&#7919;ng ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p h&#7907;p l&yacute; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7919;ng k&#7929; n&#259;ng c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t cho c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c &#273;&oacute;.</p>
<p>Ph&#7847;n danh s&aacute;ch c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c c&#7911;a trang web gi&aacute;o d&#7909;c Treehouse l&agrave; m&#7897;t v&iacute; d&#7909;. Ng&#432;&#7901;i s&aacute;ng l&#7853;p Ryan Carson n&oacute;i r&#7857;ng s&#7913; m&#7879;nh c&#7911;a c&ocirc;ng ty &ocirc;ng l&agrave; d&#7841;y c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; cho to&agrave;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i. &#272;i&#7873;u &#273;&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; ngh&#297;a l&agrave; t&#7845;t c&#7843; m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#7873;u n&ecirc;n tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh m&#7897;t l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n &ndash; ch&#7881; c&#7847;n hi&#7875;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7913;c m&#7841;nh c&#7911;a l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh th&ocirc;i c&#361;ng &#273;&atilde; c&oacute; th&#7875; mang l&#7841;i l&#7907;i &iacute;ch cho m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i n&agrave;o &#273;&oacute; trong b&#7845;t k&#7923; ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p ho&#7863;c ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c n&agrave;o. Nh&#432;ng sau khi hi&#7875;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&oacute;, c&oacute; l&#7869; ai c&#361;ng s&#7869; &ldquo;kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n s&#7907; h&atilde;i &#273;&#7875; h&#7885;c c&aacute;ch ki&#7875;m so&aacute;t n&oacute;,&rdquo; Carson n&oacute;i.</p>
<p>M&#7863;t kh&aacute;c, Treehouse c&oacute; ti&#7873;m n&#259;ng th&uacute;c &#273;&#7849;y m&#7897;t s&#7921; nghi&#7879;p m&#7899;i cho b&#7841;n. Carson cho bi&#7871;t, c&aacute;c video h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n &#7903; &#273;&acirc;y, c&oacute; th&#7875; d&#7841;y c&aacute;c k&#7929; n&#259;ng cho m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i n&agrave;o &#273;&oacute; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c ch&#7881; trong kho&#7843;ng th&#7901;i gian 6 th&aacute;ng. M&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u c&#7911;a &ocirc;ng l&agrave; k&#7871;t n&#7889;i t&#7889;t h&#417;n c&aacute;c ngu&#7891;n t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n gi&aacute;o d&#7909;c c&#7911;a Treehouse v&#7899;i c&#417; h&#7897;i vi&#7879;c l&agrave;m ngo&agrave;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng.</p>
<p>V&iacute; d&#7909;, hi&#7879;n nay m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c tr&ecirc;n trang tuy&#7875;n d&#7909;ng v&#7851;n c&ograve;n y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u m&#7897;t t&#7845;m b&#7857;ng khoa h&#7885;c m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh, nh&#432;ng Carson n&oacute;i r&#7857;ng &ocirc;ng kh&ocirc;ng tin m&#7897;t t&#7845;m b&#7857;ng l&agrave; c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7875; tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh m&#7897;t chuy&ecirc;n gia c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; gi&#7887;i (v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tuy&#7875;n d&#7909;ng), v&agrave; &ocirc;ng l&#432;u &yacute; r&#7857;ng kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i ai c&#361;ng c&oacute; &#273;&#7911; ti&#7873;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;i h&#7885;c &#273;&#7841;i h&#7885;c. Trong t&#432;&#417;ng lai, danh s&aacute;ch vi&#7879;c l&agrave;m c&oacute; th&#7875; y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u &#7913;ng vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; bao nhi&ecirc;u &#273;i&#7875;m trong m&#7897;t th&#7875; lo&#7841;i n&agrave;o &#273;&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c d&#7841;y tr&ecirc;n Treehouse (nh&#432; Ruby hay HTML) m&agrave; c&aacute;c &#7913;ng vi&ecirc;n c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i c&oacute;.</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7051" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lines-of-code.jpg" alt="lines-of-code" width="2235" height="1500" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lines-of-code.jpg 2235w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lines-of-code-300x201.jpg 300w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lines-of-code-768x515.jpg 768w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lines-of-code-1024x687.jpg 1024w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lines-of-code-696x467.jpg 696w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lines-of-code-1068x717.jpg 1068w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lines-of-code-626x420.jpg 626w" sizes="(max-width: 2235px) 100vw, 2235px"></p>
<p>B&#7897; Lao &#272;&#7897;ng Hoa K&#7923; cho bi&#7871;t &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2020 th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng M&#7929; s&#7869; c&oacute; <a href="http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/news/download/presskits/citizenship/MSNTS.pdf" target="_blank">1,2 tri&#7879;u vi&#7879;c l&agrave;m v&#7873; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh c&#7847;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7845;p &#273;&#7847;y.</a></p>
<p>&ldquo;C&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i l&agrave; ph&#7843;i hi&#7875;u r&otilde; nh&#7919;ng vi&#7879;c l&agrave;m ngo&agrave;i kia y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u g&igrave; v&agrave; l&agrave;m th&#7871; n&agrave;o &#273;&#7875; d&#7841;y h&#7885;c vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u &#273;&oacute;,&rdquo; Carson n&oacute;i. Ruby v&agrave; Javascript l&agrave; hai ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh hi&#7879;n &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u nhi&#7873;u nh&#7845;t trong danh s&aacute;ch tuy&#7875;n d&#7909;ng, v&igrave; v&#7853;y Treehouse c&#361;ng &#273;ang cung c&#7845;p gi&aacute;o tr&igrave;nh gi&#7843;ng d&#7841;y c&#7843; hai c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; n&agrave;y.</p>
<p>&#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng l&#7901;i ch&#7881; tr&iacute;ch c&#7911;a Somers v&#7873; vi&#7879;c c&aacute;c l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tr&#7843; l&#432;&#417;ng qu&aacute; cao cho nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; h&#7885; cung c&#7845;p ra th&#7871; gi&#7899;i, Carson l&#432;u &yacute; r&#7857;ng, c&#361;ng nh&#432; <a href="http://vinacode.net/2014/06/16/day-lap-trinh-truc-tuyen/" target="_blank">c&aacute;c trang web gi&aacute;o d&#7909;c tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n</a> kh&aacute;c bao g&#7891;m Treehouse, Codecademy v&agrave; Udacity d&#7841;y l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh cho h&#7885;c vi&ecirc;n v&#7899;i m&#7897;t chi ph&iacute; h&#7907;p l&yacute; trong th&#7901;i gian ng&#7855;n, th&igrave; l&#432;&#7907;ng cung v&agrave; c&#7847;u v&#7873; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n s&#7869; s&#7899;m c&acirc;n b&#7857;ng tr&#7903; l&#7841;i. V&agrave; ch&uacute;ng ta s&#7869; th&#7845;y m&#7913;c l&#432;&#417;ng gi&#7843;m xu&#7889;ng &ndash; nh&#432;ng kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; th&#7845;p, Carson n&oacute;i.</p>
<p>Kh&#7843; n&#259;ng c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; hi&#7879;n nay l&agrave;m cho &#273;i&#7873;u &#273;&oacute; nhanh ch&oacute;ng v&agrave; d&#7877; d&agrave;ng tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh hi&#7879;n th&#7921;c, ch&uacute;ng ta &#273;ang nh&igrave;n th&#7845;y r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;m thay &#273;&#7893;i th&#7871; gi&#7899;i. Nh&#432;ng &#273;i&#7873;u &#273;&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873;. &ldquo;V&agrave;i n&#259;m t&#7899;i s&#7869; l&agrave; m&#7897;t th&#7901;i k&#7923; b&ugrave;ng n&#7893; nh&#7919;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m tuy&#7879;t v&#7901;i&rdquo;, &ocirc;ng n&oacute;i.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Techtalk via <a href="https://techmaster.vn/posts/33646/lap-trinh-vien-web-de-xin-viec-lam">Techmaster</a></span></em></p></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";s:7:"Hieu Le";s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";N;}s:4:"date";s:19:"2016-10-26 08:00:27";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}}i:4;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:68:"Một lập trình viên giỏi phải biết quản lý thời gian";s:4:"link";s:75:"http://techtalk.vn/mot-lap-trinh-vien-gioi-phai-biet-quan-ly-thoi-gian.html";s:11:"description";s:594:"<div>&ldquo;Ch&#7843; c&oacute; th&#7901;i gian l&agrave;m g&igrave; c&#7843;.&rdquo; Ch&iacute; &iacute;t th&igrave; &#273;a s&#7889; ch&uacute;ng ta c&agrave;m th&#7845;y v&#7853;y &#273;&uacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng? Kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; th&#7901;i gian &#273;&#7875; h&#7885;c t&#7853;p m&#7885;i th&#7913; b&#7841;n ngh&#297; b&#7841;n c&#7847;n h&#7885;c &#273;&#7875; v&#432;&#7907;t l&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n b&#7847;y ng&#7921;a. Ch&#7843; c&oacute; th&#7901;i quan &#273;&#7875; quay l&#7841;i v&agrave; refactor c&aacute;i m&#7899; code c&#361; c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh. D&ugrave; [&hellip;]</div>";s:7:"content";s:24336:"<div><p>&ldquo;Ch&#7843; c&oacute; th&#7901;i gian l&agrave;m g&igrave; c&#7843;.&rdquo; Ch&iacute; &iacute;t th&igrave; &#273;a s&#7889; ch&uacute;ng ta c&agrave;m th&#7845;y v&#7853;y &#273;&uacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng? Kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; th&#7901;i gian &#273;&#7875; h&#7885;c t&#7853;p m&#7885;i th&#7913; b&#7841;n ngh&#297; b&#7841;n c&#7847;n h&#7885;c &#273;&#7875; v&#432;&#7907;t l&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n b&#7847;y ng&#7921;a. Ch&#7843; c&oacute; th&#7901;i quan &#273;&#7875; quay l&#7841;i v&agrave; refactor c&aacute;i m&#7899; code c&#361; c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh. D&ugrave; g&igrave; th&igrave; ch&uacute;ng c&#361;ng ch&#7841;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c (c&oacute; v&#7867; th&#7871;) v&agrave; deadline &#273;ang g&#7847;n k&#7873; r&#7891;i. Ch&#7843; c&oacute; th&#7901;i gian &#273;&#7875; vi&#7871;t c&aacute;i unit test n&agrave;o c&#7843;. Ch&#7843; c&oacute; th&#7901;i gian vi&#7871;t document hay comment cho ng&#432;&#7901;i &ldquo;k&#7871; nghi&#7879;p&rdquo; m&#7899; code c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. Ch&#7843; c&oacute; th&#7901;i gian suy ngh&#297;. Ch&#7843; c&oacute; th&#7901;i gian th&#7903; lu&ocirc;n. Ch&#7843; c&oacute; t&yacute; th&#7901;i gian g&igrave; h&#7871;t!</p>
<p>&#7914; th&igrave;&hellip; N&#7871;u b&#7841;n &#273;&#7885;c b&agrave;i vi&#7871;t n&agrave;y. &#272;&#7843;m b&#7841;o b&#7841;n s&#7869; th&#7845;y m&igrave;nh c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u th&#7901;i gian h&#417;n &#273;&#7875; d&agrave;nh cho nh&#7919;ng vi&#7879;c th&#7921;c s&#7921; quan tr&#7885;ng &#273;&#7845;y.</p>
<p>T&ocirc;i t&#7915;ng ngh&#297;, &#273;&#7875; tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh m&#7897;t l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;, t&ocirc;i ph&#7843;i l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c &#273;&#7871;n ki&#7879;t s&#7913;c m&#7899;i th&ocirc;i. V&agrave; s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e, c&#361;ng nh&#432; quan h&#7879; gia &#273;&igrave;nh, b&#7841;n b&egrave; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u r&#7841;n n&#7913;t. N&#259;m &#273;&uacute;t k&#7871;t d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y v&#7873; vi&#7879;c qu&#7843;n l&yacute; th&#7901;i gian &#273;&atilde; gi&uacute;p &#273;&#7905; t&ocirc;i r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u tr&ocirc;ng cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng.</p>
<h3><b>1. &#272;&#7875; b&aacute;m tr&#7909; b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i h&#7885;c h&#7871;t m&#7885;i th&#7913;.</b></h3>
<figure style="width: 400px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="size-full" src="https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*nlHiraEMnpECFoi3_nIV4g.gif" alt="Kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n &#273;&acirc;u!" width="400" height="300"><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n &#273;&acirc;u!</figcaption></figure><p>Hi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n, l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n th&igrave; ph&#7843;i lu&ocirc;n lu&ocirc;n c&#7853;p nh&#7853;t, &#273;&acirc;y l&agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; b&agrave;n c&atilde;i, nh&#432;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n t&#7853;p trung h&#7885;c t&#7853;p c&#7911;a b&#7841;n s&#7869; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng r&#7845;t l&#7899;n &#273;&#7871;n th&#7901;i gian c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7877; th&agrave;nh th&#7909;c k&#7929; n&#259;ng &#273;&oacute;.</p>
<p>Tr&#432;&#7899;c h&#7871;t, &#273;&#7915;ng qu&aacute; m&ecirc; m&#7849;n nh&#7919;ng ti&ecirc;u &#273;&#7873; v&#7899;i l&#7901;i ra m&#7855;t chu&#7849;n m&#7899;i g&igrave; &#273;&oacute; m&#7895;i 37 gi&acirc;y. &#272;a s&#7889; c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879;, framewok c&#361;ng nh&#432; t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng m&#7899;i s&#7869; hi&#7871;m khi n&agrave;o t&#7841;o &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng l&#7899;n v&agrave; b&#7841;n s&#7869; ch&#7843; c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i bi&#7871;t v&#7873; ch&uacute;ng l&agrave;m g&igrave;. Nh&#7919;ng c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879;/framework m&#7899;i d&ugrave; c&oacute; &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&uacute;t ti&#7871;ng t&#259;m c&#361;ng m&#7845;t c&agrave;ng nhi&#7873;u th&#7901;i gian h&#417;n n&#7919;a &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; th&#7875; &aacute;p d&#7909;ng r&#7897;ng r&atilde;i &ndash; v&agrave; th&#432;&#417;ng gia s&#7869; l&agrave;m b&#7841;n tin t&#432;&#7903;ng. Nhi&#7873;u c&ocirc;ng ty r&#7845;t quan t&acirc;m v&agrave;o m&#7843;ng c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879;, v&agrave; ngo&agrave;i m&#7897;t m&#7899; tech startup nh&#7887; y&#7871;u, h&#7885; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; r&#7867; v&agrave;o g&oacute;c nh&#7887; x&iacute;u nh&#432; v&#7853;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&acirc;u. N&ecirc;n &#273;&#7915;ng lo l&#7855;ng, s&#7921; nghi&#7879;p c&#7911;a b&#7841;n v&#7851;n c&ograve;n kh&aacute; an to&agrave;n.</p>
<p>H&atilde;y t&#7853;p trung s&#7921; nghi&#7879;p c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh xoay quanh ba ph&#7841;m vi sau, theo th&#7913; t&#7921; &#432;u ti&ecirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng:</p>
<ol><li><strong>N&#7873;n t&#7843;ng</strong> &ndash; b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; ti&#7871;p thu k&#7929; n&#259;ng m&#7899;i nhanh h&#417;n n&#7871;u &#273;&atilde; n&#7855;ng r&otilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng c&#7847;n c&oacute;. V&iacute; d&#7909; nh&#432;, n&#7871;u b&#7841;n hi&#7873;u r&#7845;t s&acirc;u v&#7873; JavaSciprt, b&#7841;n ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c&oacute; th&#7875; l&agrave;m ch&#7911; b&#7845;t c&#7913; JavaScript framework n&agrave;o v&#7899;i t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n hi&#7875;u r&otilde; Object Oriented Programming, b&#7841;n c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; nhanh ch&oacute;ng th&agrave;nh th&#7841;o c&aacute;c ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; h&#432;&#7899;ng object kh&aacute;c. Ch&uacute; tr&#7885;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c v&agrave;o n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng c&#417; b&#7841;n s&#7869; gi&uacute;p b&#7841;n h&#7885;c t&#7853;p hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; h&#417;n g&#7845;p 10 l&#7847;n. Lu&ocirc;n lu&ocirc;n &#273;&#7863;t n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng l&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n t&#7845;t c&#7843;.</li>
<li><strong>Phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n/t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng m&#7899;i nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; b&#7841;n d&ugrave;ng nhi&#7873;u nh&#7845;t</strong> &ndash; S&#7869; c&oacute; m&#7897;t v&agrave;i th&#7913; c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; n&agrave;o &#273;&oacute; b&#7841;n &#273;ang d&ugrave;ng h&#7857;ng ng&agrave;y. &#272;&acirc;y ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; &ldquo;ki&#7871;m c&#417;m&rdquo; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. Khi nh&#7919;ng c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; n&agrave;y xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n m&#7899;i, B&#7841;n n&ecirc;n d&agrave;nh &iacute;t th&#7901;i gian t&igrave;m hi&#7875;u th&#7917;.</li>
<li><strong>Nh&#7919;ng c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; hot &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7919;ng &ocirc;ng l&#7899;n tr&ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7895; tr&#7907;, ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n</strong> &ndash; N&#7871;u m&#7897;t c&ocirc;ng ty l&#7899;n, ch&#7863;t ch&#7869; nh&#432; Google, Facebook, hay Microsoft c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; m&#7899;i, v&agrave; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u thu h&uacute;t &iacute;t nhi&#7873;u ch&uacute; &yacute;, th&igrave; b&#7841;n n&ecirc;n t&igrave;m hi&#7875;u th&#7917;. C&oacute; &#273;&#7871;n h&agrave;ng tr&#259;m framework JavaScript ch&#7853;t v&#7853;t t&igrave;m ch&#7895; &#273;&#7913;ng, v&agrave; ch&#7881; v&#7899;i s&#7921; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n c&#7911;a Angular v&agrave; React m&agrave; t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;i t&ecirc;n kh&aacute;c &#273;&atilde; tr&ocirc;i v&agrave;o qu&ecirc;n l&atilde;ng. &Yacute; t&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; s&#7869; ch&#7843; bao gi&#7901; &ldquo;anh t&agrave;i&rdquo; b&#7895;ng d&#432;ng xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n v&agrave; thay &#273;&#7893;i c&#7843; b&#7913;c tranh c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879;, nh&#432;ng t&#7927; l&#7879; n&agrave;y th&#7853;t s&#7921; l&agrave; v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng nh&#7887; b&eacute;.</li>
</ol><p>B&#7841;n lu&ocirc;n n&ecirc;n d&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n trong l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; h&#7885;c t&#7853;p. Kho&#7843;ng th&#7901;i gian n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n nhi&#7873;u, th&#7853;m ch&iacute; ch&#7881; 25 ph&uacute;t &#273;&#7885;c v&agrave; th&#7917; nghi&#7879;m m&#7895;i ng&agrave;y c&#361;ng qu&aacute; &#273;&#7911; r&#7891;i.</p>
<p><b>2. Vi&#7871;t code t&#7889;t c&ograve;n nhanh h&#417;n vi&#7871;t code d&#7903;, NH&#431;NG ch&uacute;ng ta l&#7841;i c&oacute; </b><b><i>c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c</i></b><b> ng&#432;&#7907;c l&#7841;i.</b></p>
<figure style="width: 400px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="size-full" src="https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*T_iEqRX_YzZjmQeaRgk2mA.gif" alt="Th&#7901;i gian l&agrave; m&#7897;t v&ograve;ng tr&ograve;n d&#7865;p. " width="400" height="220"><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Th&#7901;i gian l&agrave; m&#7897;t v&ograve;ng tr&ograve;n d&#7865;p.</figcaption></figure><p>C&oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u b&#7841;n c&oacute; suy ngh&#297; ch&#7881; c&#7847;n vi&#7871;t code c&#7911;a t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng m&#7899;i m&agrave; ch&#7841;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&agrave; xong r&#7891;i. Nh&#432;ng &#273;&acirc;y s&#7869; ch&#7881; l&agrave; m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n nh&#7887; trong s&#7889; th&#7901;i gian m&agrave; b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; th&ocirc;i. B&#7841;n c&ograve;n ph&#7843;i b&#7887; th&#7901;i gian c&ocirc;ng s&#7913;c debug t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng, r&#7891;i refactor, r&#7891;i ph&#7843;i tinh ch&#7881;nh code &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t nh&#7919;ng quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh thi&#7871;t k&#7871; s&agrave;i l&#7847;m khi b&#7841;n tri&#7875;n khai t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng &#273;&oacute;. Khi b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u bi&#7871;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; th&#7901;i gian c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;y, th&igrave; b&#7841;n s&#7869; ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng r&otilde; r&agrave;ng, d&#7847;n d&#7847;n b&#7841;n s&#7869; g&#7863;p &iacute;t l&#7895;i h&#417;n v&agrave; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7919;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871; t&#7889;t h&#417;n, v&agrave; th&#7901;i gian b&#7841;n b&#7887; ra c&ograve;n s&#7869; h&#417;n c&#7843; x&#7913;ng &#273;&aacute;ng n&#7919;a.</p>
<p>B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; l&agrave;m hai &#273;i&#7873;u sau &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m l&#7895;i trong code v&agrave; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; t&#7889;t h&#417;n.</p>
<ol><li><b>L&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh l&#7845;y test l&agrave;m trung t&acirc;m</b>. Vi&#7871;t test tr&#432;&#7899;c, sau &#273;&oacute; vi&#7871;t code th&#7887;a m&atilde;n test. Nh&#432; v&#7853;y b&#7841;n s&#7869; c&oacute; th&#7901;i gian c&#7845;u tr&uacute;c code theo h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7877; test h&#417;n, cho ra nh&#7919;ng function &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n h&#417;n, v&#7899;i &iacute;t dependencies h&#417;n.</li>
<li><b>L&#7889;i thi&#7871;t k&#7871; quay l&#7841;i</b>. &#272;&#7915;ng ph&iacute; th&#7901;i gian ch&#7881;nh code cho ho&agrave;n h&#7843;o tr&#432;&#7899;c khi l&agrave;m cho code ch&#7841;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c. B&#7841;n s&#7869; ch&#7843; bao gi&#7901; h&igrave;nh dung &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t &#273;o&#7841;n code s&#7841;ch g&#7885;n trong &#273;&#7847;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&acirc;u. B&#7841;n ph&#7843;i ra tay g&otilde; ph&iacute;m &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c code ch&#7841;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#432; d&#7921; t&iacute;nh &#273;&atilde;. V&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; l&agrave; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n lu&ocirc;n ph&#7841;m ph&#7843;i m&#7897;t trong hai l&#7895;i sau; h&#7885; s&#7869; ph&iacute; qu&aacute; nhi&#7873;u th&#7901;i gian suy ngh&#297; m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng th&#7921;c s&#7921; l&agrave;m g&igrave; c&#7843;, ho&#7863;c h&#7885; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; &#273;&#7911; th&#7901;i gian c&#7843;i thi&#7879;n gi&#7843;i ph&aacute;p ban &#273;&#7847;u c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh. H&atilde;y &#273;i theo c&acirc;u th&#7847;n ch&uacute; k&#7923; di&#7879;u c&#7911;a Kent Beck: &ldquo;make it work, make it right, make it fast&rdquo; &ndash; v&agrave; t&#7845;t nhi&ecirc;n c&#361;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&uacute;ng theo th&#7913; t&#7921; n&agrave;y r&#7891;i.
<div class="MediaCard-mediaContainer js-cspForcedStyle" data-style="padding-bottom: 75.0000%"><a href="https://vietnamwebsummit.com/vi/home/" target="_blank"><img class="td-animation-stack-type0-2 aligncenter wp-image-9899" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Vietnam-web-summit.png" width="550" height="280" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Vietnam-web-summit.png 629w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Vietnam-web-summit-300x153.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px"></a><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong>Tham gia c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh Web l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t Vi&#7879;t Nam: <a href="http://vietnamwebsummit.com/">Vietnamwebsummit.com</a></strong></span></div>
</li>
</ol><h3><b>3. L&agrave;m vi&#7879;c 24/7 gi&#7889;ng kh&ugrave;ng ch&#7913; ch&#7843; ph&#7843;i ng&#432;&#7901;i h&ugrave;ng. H&atilde;y qu&#7843;n l&yacute; k&#7923; v&#7885;ng &#273;i th&ocirc;i.<br></b></h3>
<figure style="width: 480px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img src="https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*NyLgzD71S8ZmsZ1QWRTYtw.gif" width="480" height="270"><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">H&#7871;t gi&#7901; l&agrave;m. L&agrave;m ti&#7871;p th&ocirc;i!</figcaption></figure><p>Ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c t&ocirc;i t&#7915;ng &#273;&#7891;ng t&igrave;nh v&agrave; c&#7855;m &#273;&#7847;u v&agrave;o l&#7883;ch c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c d&agrave;y &#273;&#7863;c m&agrave; s&#7871;p v&agrave; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng giao ph&oacute;. T&ocirc;i s&#7907; t&#7915; ch&#7889;i. T&ocirc;i s&#7907; l&agrave;m ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&aacute;c ph&#7853;t l&ograve;ng. T&ocirc;i s&#7869; l&agrave;m m&#7885;i gi&aacute; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&#7871;t qu&#7843;. &#272;&atilde; c&oacute; th&#7901;i t&ocirc;i ng&#7911; g&#7909;c li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c tr&ecirc;n b&agrave;n l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, b&#7847;u b&#7841;n v&#7899;i c&#7889;c cafein &#273;&#7875; s&#7889;ng s&oacute;t h&#417;n 40+ ti&#7871;ng &#273;&#7891;ng h&#7891; code li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c.</p>
<p>M&#7899;i &#273;&#7847;u, t&ocirc;i l&agrave; ng&ocirc;i sao s&aacute;ng ch&oacute;i. T&ocirc;i s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c v&#7895; vai hoan ngh&ecirc;nh v&agrave; c&#7843;m th&#7845;y nh&#432; m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i h&ugrave;ng. Nh&#432;ng &#273;&acirc;y l&#7841;i l&agrave; m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u kh&ocirc;ng c&aacute;ch n&agrave;o gi&#7919; v&#7919;ng. C&aacute;ch l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng mang l&#7841;i hi&#7875;u qu&#7843; d&agrave;i l&acirc;u. D&#7847;n d&#7847;n, t&ocirc;i k&#7879;t s&#7913;c, b&#7879;nh t&#7853;t, m&#7879;t m&#7887;i, v&agrave; tr&#7877; deadline li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c. T&ocirc;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u &ldquo;n&#7893;i danh&rdquo; b&#7857;ng s&#7921; b&#7845;t &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; thi&#7871;u uy t&iacute;n c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh.</p>
<p>Sau n&agrave;y t&ocirc;i &#273;&atilde; d&#7847;n hi&#7875;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, ng&#432;&#7901;i h&ugrave;ng th&#7853;t s&#7921; l&agrave; m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh m&agrave; b&#7841;n lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; th&#7875; tin t&#432;&#7903;ng. H&#7885; n&oacute;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&igrave; s&#7869; l&agrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, v&agrave; h&#7885; s&#7869; l&agrave;m nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; h&#7885; n&oacute;i. V&agrave; c&aacute;ch duy nh&#7845;t tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh ng&#432;&#7901;i h&ugrave;ng nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;y l&agrave;: qu&#7843;n l&yacute; k&#7923; v&#7885;ng.</p>
<p>B&#7841;n c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i ki&#7875;m so&aacute;t l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh, &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; th&#7875; lu&ocirc;n lu&ocirc;n cho ra k&#7871;t qu&#7843; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cao v&agrave; k&#7883;p th&#7901;i. Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; k&#7923; v&#7885;ng m&#7899;i &#273;&#7847;u s&#7869; v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng kh&oacute; kh&#259;n. B&#7841;n s&#7869; ph&#7843;i h&#7885;c c&aacute;ch t&#7915; ch&#7889;i, v&agrave; h&#7885;c c&aacute;ch &#273;&#7849;y ng&#432;&#7907;c tr&#7903; l&#7841;i.</p>
<p>Ban &#273;&#7847;u, s&#7871;p c&#7911;a b&#7841;n ho&#7863;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s&#7869; c&#7843;m th&#7845;y kh&ocirc;ng vui v&igrave; h&agrave;nh &#273;&#7897;ng kh&aacute;ng c&#7921; n&agrave;y, nh&#432;ng khi b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; ch&#7913;ng minh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m n&agrave;y r&#7845;t &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; &#273;&aacute;ng tin c&#7853;y, m&#7885;i th&#7913; s&#7869; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u thay &#273;&#7893;i.</p>
<p>D&#7847;n d&#7849;n, nh&#7919;ng l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n kh&aacute;c s&#7869; l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c ch&#7853;m tr&#7877;, c&#7849;u th&#7843;, ho&#7863;c ki&#7879;t s&#7913;c v&agrave; m&#7845;t uy t&iacute;n. V&agrave; b&#7841;n s&#7869; v&#432;&#7907;t l&ecirc;n l&agrave;m ng&#432;&#7901;i h&ugrave;ng th&#7853;t s&#7921; trong team. Th&#7921;c ra, khi bi&#7871;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y,t&ocirc;i &#273;&atilde; tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng consultant &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7855;n &#273;&oacute;n nh&#7845;t tr&ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng. T&ocirc;i g&#7847;y d&#7921;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c danh ti&#7871;ng lan r&#7897;ng nh&#7901; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng v&agrave; s&#7921; &#273;&uacute;ng gi&#7901; c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh, v&igrave; t&ocirc;i &#273;&atilde; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; k&#7923; v&#7885;ng r&#7845;t th&agrave;nh th&#7841;o.</p>
<h3><b>4. Kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&uacute;c &ldquo;ch&#7881;nh&rdquo; code n&agrave;o c&#361;ng mang l&#7841;i c&ugrave;ng k&#7871;t qu&#7843;.</b></h3>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full" src="https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*JMk2wpkTz9SKzs1D9s7-CA.png" alt="" width="500" height="375"></p>
<p>Th&#7901;i gian l&agrave; m&#7897;t d&#7841;ng &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;. V&agrave; nh&#432; m&#7885;i d&#7841;ng &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; kh&aacute;c, b&#7841;n lu&ocirc;n mong &#273;&#7907;i ROI (return on investment &ndash; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;). Ch&iacute; &iacute;t b&#7841;n c&#361;ng ph&#7843;n thu l&#7841;i b&#7857;ng, v&agrave; hi v&#7885;ng l&agrave; h&#417;n nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; &#273;&atilde; b&#7887; ra.</p>
<p>Ch&uacute;ng ta &#273;&atilde; nh&#7855;c &#273;&#7871;n c&acirc;u th&#7847;n ch&uacute; &ldquo;make it work, make it right, make it fast.&rdquo; Nh&#432;ng c&acirc;u n&agrave;y v&#7851;n c&ograve;n c&aacute;i b&#7851;y: &ldquo;right&rdquo; kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; ho&agrave;n h&#7843;o, v&agrave; &ldquo;fast&rdquo; c&#361;ng kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; nhanh h&#7871;t m&#7913;c c&oacute; th&#7875;.</p>
<p>&ldquo;Right&rdquo; ngh&#297;a l&agrave; code s&#7869; l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; d&#7877; refactor h&#417;n. &ldquo;Fast&rdquo; ngh&#297;a l&agrave; t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; th&#7921;c thi s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng t&#7841;o c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c ti&ecirc;u c&#7921;c &#273;&#7871;n tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng t&#7893;ng quan. &#272;i&#7873;u quan tr&#7885;ng nh&#7845;t l&agrave; &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n mang l&#7841;i c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c &ldquo;nhanh&rdquo; &#273;&#7871;n v&#7899;i ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng.</p>
<p>V&#7853;y n&ecirc;n, &#273;&#7915;ng ph&iacute; th&#7901;i gian t&#7881;a t&oacute;t m&#7897;t ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng hi&#7875;m khi n&agrave;o s&#7917; d&#7909;ng, hay b&#7887; c&ocirc;ng tinh ch&#7881;nh &#7913;ng ch&#7881; &#273;&#7875; nhanh h&#417;n m&#7897;t ch&uacute;t so v&#7899;i kho&#7843;ng th&#7901;i gian nh&aacute;y m&#7855;t c&#7911;a m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i (~300ms). V&agrave; c&#361;ng &#273;&#7915;ng ph&iacute; th&#7901;i gian c&#7889; refactor code &#273;&atilde; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, &#273;&atilde; c&oacute; c&#7845;u tr&uacute;c ch&#7863;t, ch&#7881; v&igrave; b&#7841;n m&#7899;i h&#7885;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&#7929; thu&#7853;t m&#7899;i n&agrave;o &#273;&oacute; th&ocirc;i th&uacute;c b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i quay l&#7841;i v&agrave; thay &#273;&#7893;i m&#7885;i th&#7913; b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; l&agrave;m.</p>
<h3><b>5. C&oacute; gi&#7901; ngh&#7881;, b&#7841;n s&#7869; l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; h&#417;n.</b></h3>
<figure style="width: 450px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img src="https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*tREYaPTUYGW_LAbdOBKbaw.gif" width="450" height="170"><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Dude, relax.</figcaption></figure><p>&#272;&acirc;y l&agrave; b&agrave;i h&#7885;c r&#7845;t kh&oacute; ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i t&ocirc;i. L&agrave;m th&#7871; n&agrave;o m&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; n&#259;ng su&#7845;t h&#417;n khi l&#7841;i kh&ocirc;ng d&agrave;nh th&#7901;i gian l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c? Kh&oacute; tin, nh&#432;ng v&#7851;n &#273;&uacute;ng &#273;&#7845;y.</p>
<p>Theo Allison Gabriel, ph&oacute; gi&aacute;o s&#432; qu&#7843;n tr&#7883; h&#7885;c chuy&ecirc;n v&#7873; nhu c&#7847;u tuy&#7875;n d&#7909;ng v&agrave; &#273;&#7897;ng vi&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n l&#7921;c t&#7841;i &nbsp;Virginia Commonwealth University, &ldquo;R&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u ch&#7881; ra r&#7857;ng ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; ngu&#7891;n l&#7921;c tinh th&#7847;n r&#7845;t h&#7841;n ch&#7871;. Khi b&#7841;n li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c r&uacute;t c&#7841;n ngu&#7891;n l&#7921;c n&agrave;y, b&#7841;n s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; ph&aacute;t huy h&#7871;t n&#259;ng s&#7913;c v&#7889;n c&oacute; c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n h&#7871;t ngu&#7891;n l&#7921;c, n&#259;ng su&#7845;t c&#361;ng s&#7869; khuynh gi&#7843;m. T&#7915; &#273;&oacute; &#273;&#7897; b&#7873;n b&#7881; v&agrave; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; trong c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c c&#361;ng gi&#7843;m theo.&rdquo;</p>
<p>Trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, c&aacute;c ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n s&#7869; l&agrave;m n&#7843;y sinh m&#7897;t chu&#7895;i ph&#7843;n &#7913;ng c&#259;ng th&#7859;ng, nh&#432; stress, m&#7879;t m&#7887;i, v&agrave; c&#7843;m x&uacute;c ti&ecirc;u c&#7921;c. Nh&#7919;ng ph&#7843;n &#7913;ng n&agrave;y l&agrave; nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n khi&#7871;n b&#7841;n m&#7845;t s&#7921; t&#7853;p trung, m&#7845;t &#273;i ngu&#7891;n l&#7921;c s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e v&agrave; tinh th&#7847;n c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh.</p>
<p>Kh&#7843; n&#259;ng k&#7927; lu&#7853;t trong ng&agrave;y c&#7911;a n&atilde;o b&#7897; s&#7869; d&#7847;n thui ch&#7897;t &#273;i sau m&#7895;i l&#7847;n ta t&#7921; ki&#7875;m so&aacute;t b&#7843;n th&acirc;n. V&agrave; tr&#432;&#7899;c s&#7921; thui ch&#7897;t n&agrave;y, c&#417; th&#7875; c&#7847;n th&#7901;i gian &#273;&#7875; b&#7893; sung. B&#7857;ng kh&ocirc;ng, n&atilde;o b&#7897; s&#7869; kh&oacute; c&oacute; th&#7875; t&#7853;p trung, ch&#259;m ch&uacute; v&agrave; gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c.</p>
<p>N&atilde;o b&#7897; v&agrave; c&#417; th&#7875; c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i ngh&#7881; ng&#417;i, v&agrave; d&ugrave; b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n hay kh&ocirc;ng, chuy&#7879;n &#273;&#7845;y c&#361;ng s&#7869; s&#7843;y ra. H&atilde;y l&ecirc;n k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch v&agrave; lu&ocirc;n d&agrave;nh th&#7901;i gian trong ng&agrave;y cho nh&#7919;ng l&uacute;c ngh&#7881; ng&#417;i n&agrave;y. Nh&#432; v&#7853;y. b&#7841;n v&#7915;a c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#432; gi&#7843;n, v&#7915;a tr&aacute;nh c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c t&#7895;i l&#7895;i. B&#7841;n c&#361;ng s&#7869; &iacute;t b&#7887; ngang h&#417;n v&#7899;i suy ngh&#297;: &ldquo;s&#7855;p &#273;&#7871;n gi&#7901; ngh&#7881; r&#7891;i, l&agrave;m m&#7897;t ch&uacute;t n&#7919;a th&ocirc;i.&rdquo;</p>
<h3><b>&#272;&#7885;c th&ecirc;m &#7903; &#273;&acirc;u</b></h3>
<p>&#272;&#7875; gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c b&#7841;n h&igrave;nh dung r&otilde; r&agrave;ng h&#417;n n&#7919;a, t&ocirc;i &#273;&atilde; t&#7893;ng h&#7907;p l&#7841;i m&#7897;t lo&#7841;t t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n chi ti&#7871;t, h&#7919;u &iacute;ch v&agrave; mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; (g&#7891;m video, h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n v&agrave; website) v&#7873; nh&#7919;ng ki&#7871;n th&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7855;c &#273;&#7871;n trong b&agrave;i vi&#7871;t. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; xem th&#7917;<a href="https://devmastery.com/signup/time/index.html"> t&#7841;i &#273;&acirc;y.</a></p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em>Techtalk via <a href="https://medium.freecodecamp.com/finding-time-to-become-a-better-developer-eebc154881b2#.erqchxa8h">medium</a></em></p></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Thien Bui";s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";N;}s:4:"date";s:19:"2016-10-26 07:00:10";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}}i:5;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:65:"Điều gì tạo nên một Software Architect chuyên nghiệp?";s:4:"link";s:76:"http://techtalk.vn/dieu-gi-tao-nen-mot-software-architect-chuyen-nghiep.html";s:11:"description";s:608:"<div>Software Architect l&agrave; m&#7897;t v&#7883; tr&iacute; r&#7845;t n&oacute;ng b&#7887;ng v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nhi&#7873;u c&ocirc;ng ty ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u s&#259;n &#273;&oacute;n. Nhi&#7873;u Senior Software Engineer c&#361;ng quan t&acirc;m v&agrave; mu&#7889;n d&#7883;ch chuy&#7875;n sang v&#7883; tr&iacute; n&agrave;y. Nh&#432;ng &#273;i&#7873;u g&igrave; t&#7841;o n&ecirc;n m&#7897;t Software Architect chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p? M&#7897;t ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c s&#432; ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m (Software Architect) [&hellip;]</div>";s:7:"content";s:10245:"<div><p><em><strong>Software Architect l&agrave; m&#7897;t v&#7883; tr&iacute; r&#7845;t n&oacute;ng b&#7887;ng v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nhi&#7873;u c&ocirc;ng ty ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u s&#259;n &#273;&oacute;n. Nhi&#7873;u Senior Software Engineer c&#361;ng quan t&acirc;m v&agrave; mu&#7889;n d&#7883;ch chuy&#7875;n sang v&#7883; tr&iacute; n&agrave;y. Nh&#432;ng &#273;i&#7873;u g&igrave; t&#7841;o n&ecirc;n m&#7897;t Software Architect chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p?</strong></em></p>
<p>M&#7897;t ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c s&#432; ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m (Software Architect) &#7903; c&ocirc;ng ty c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u tr&ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i th&#432;&#7901;ng l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i c&oacute; m&#7897;t t&#432; duy xu&#7845;t s&#7855;c v&agrave; lu&ocirc;n nh&igrave;n &ldquo;Big picture&rdquo;. H&#7885; hi&#7875;u nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t m&#7897;t v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u k&iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c kh&aacute;c nhau. H&#7885; x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh c&aacute;c h&#7879; th&#7889;ng th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n b&ecirc;n trong m&#7897;t h&#7879; th&#7889;ng t&#7893;ng th&#7875;, l&agrave;m sao c&aacute;c h&#7879; th&#7889;ng th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n giao ti&#7871;p h&agrave;i ho&agrave; v&#7899;i nhau, v&agrave; l&agrave;m sao &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o ra m&#7897;t h&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;&aacute;ng tin c&#7853;y v&agrave; &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7879;u su&#7845;t theo y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u. Ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c s&#432; ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng chuy&ecirc;n gia trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c, &#273;&atilde; t&#7915;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871;, tri&#7875;n khai nhi&#7873;u s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m kh&aacute;c nhau.</p>
<p>&#272;&acirc;u l&agrave; y&#7871;u t&#7889; t&#7841;o ta m&#7897;t Software Architect chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p:</p>
<p><strong>1) L&agrave; m&#7897;t chuy&ecirc;n gia trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c &ndash; domain expert</strong>: H&#7885; c&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; hi&#7875;u bi&#7871;t &#273;&#7911; r&#7897;ng v&#7873; l&#297;nh v&#7921;c ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m &#273;&#7875; bi&#7871;t nh&#7919;ng th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n, c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; n&agrave;o c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c. H&#7885; hi&#7875;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; &#273;&aacute;nh &#273;&#7893;i gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c thu&#7897;c t&iacute;nh ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng &ndash; quality attributes nh&#432;: reliability, flexibility, performance,&hellip; v&agrave; d&#7877; d&agrave;ng tri&#7875;n khai v&agrave; m&#7903; r&#7897;ng trong t&#432;&#417;ng lai. H&#7885; lu&ocirc;n &#273;&#432;a ra nh&#7919;ng ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; s&#7921; ch&#7885;n l&#7921;a thi&#7871;t k&#7871; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u v&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;a ra c&aacute;c h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n cho ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&aacute;c ch&#7885;n l&#7921;a thi&#7871;t k&#7871; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u c&#7911;a chuy&ecirc;n vi&ecirc;n ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch nghi&#7879;p v&#7909;.</p>
<p><strong>2) L&agrave; m&#7897;t c&#7889; v&#7845;n</strong>: Th&ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng m&#7909;c &#273;&iacute;ch c&#7911;a h&#7879; th&#7889;ng l&agrave; lu m&#7901;. C&aacute;c &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t cho c&aacute;c h&agrave;nh vi v&agrave; c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c suy ngh&#297; th&ocirc;ng su&#7889;t. M&#7897;t ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c s&#432; ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m c&oacute; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;a ra h&#432;&#7899;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871; &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t c&aacute;c v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; v&agrave; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n c&aacute;c k&#7929; s&#432; l&agrave;m sao &#273;&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n thi&#7871;t k&#7871; chi ti&#7871;t trong t&#432;&#417;ng lai. H&#7885; hi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7853;n v&#7873; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng v&agrave; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch c&aacute;c thu&#7897;c t&iacute;nh c&#7911;a h&#7879; th&#7889;ng v&agrave; c&aacute;c h&agrave;nh vi trong ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p ti&#7871;p c&#7853;n &#273;&#7875; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng h&#7879; th&#7889;ng. H&#7885; &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t c&aacute;c ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&agrave; ch&#7913;ng minh c&aacute;ch t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p th&#7879; th&#7889;ng theo t&#7915;ng ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p c&#7909; th&#7875;. M&#7897;t ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c s&#432; ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p &#273;i&#7873;u h&#432;&#7899;ng s&#7921; &#273;&#7891;ng thu&#7853;n &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m th&#7871; n&agrave;o h&#7879; th&#7889;ng, c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n c&#7911;a h&#7879; th&#7889;ng c&#7847;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; v&agrave; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#273;&#7875; &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u, k&#7875; c&aacute;c c&aacute;c t&agrave;i li&#7879;u h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n thi&#7871;t k&#7871; nh&#432; Coding Convention,&hellip;</p>
<p><strong>3) L&agrave; m&#7897;t l&atilde;nh &#273;&#7841;o k&#7929; thu&#7853;t hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;</strong>: M&#7897;t ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c s&#432; ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m l&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i xu&#7845;t s&#7855;c trong giao ti&#7871;p v&#7899;i c&aacute;c c&#7845;p kh&aacute;c nhau li&ecirc;n quan trong s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m t&#7915; CEO &#273;&#7871;n c&aacute;c c&#7845;p Software Engineer. H&#7885; bi&#7879;n minh cho m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u c&#7911;a h&#7879; th&#7889;ng, ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c h&#7879; th&#7889;ng b&#7857;ng l&#7901;i n&oacute;i ho&#7863;c t&agrave;i li&#7879;u, v&agrave; h&#7885; l&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i r&#7845;t gi&#7887;i trong vi&#7879;c vi&#7871;t c&aacute;c t&agrave;i li&#7879;u c&#7911;a h&#7879; th&#7889;ng, B&ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&oacute; h&#7885; &#273;&#432;a ra c&aacute;c gi&#7843;i ph&aacute;p &#273;&#7875; t&aacute;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m ch&iacute; ph&iacute; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&agrave; gi&#7843;m r&#7911;i ro qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n. H&#7885; th&#7889;ng nh&#7845;t c&aacute;c &#273;&#7897;i trong d&#7921; &aacute;n c&#7911;a h&#7885;, &#273;&#432;a ra t&#7847;m nh&igrave;n v&#7873; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng v&agrave; gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c &#273;&#7897;i d&#7921; &aacute;n t&#7853;p trung v&agrave;o t&#7847;m nh&igrave;n, l&ocirc;i k&eacute;o m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c c&ugrave;ng nhau &#273;&#7875; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t nh&#7919;ng th&#7913; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p ch&#7863;t ch&#7869; l&#7851;n nhau.</p>
<p><strong>4) L&agrave; m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i ph&acirc;n r&atilde; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t s&#7855;c</strong>: Ph&acirc;n r&atilde; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; l&agrave; m&#7897;t k&#7929; n&#259;ng c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; nh&igrave;n v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; &#7903; c&aacute;c c&#7845;p &#273;&#7897; kh&aacute;c nhau v&agrave; chia ra nhi&#7873;u b&#432;&#7899;c v&agrave; c&aacute;c ph&#7847;n kh&aacute;c nhau &#273;&#7875; tri&#7875;n khai v&agrave; &#273;&#432;a ra h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p h&#7879; th&#7889;ng t&#7915; c&aacute;c &#273;&#7897;i d&#7921; &aacute;n kh&aacute;c nhau theo th&#7901;i gian. M&#7897;t ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c s&#432; ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p lu&ocirc;n &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t ph&#432;&#417;ng th&#7913;c ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m v&agrave; c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng c&#7909;, c&#417; s&#7903; h&#7841; t&#7847;ng c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p d&#7921; &aacute;n m&#7897;t c&aacute;ch hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;, &iacute;t r&#7911;i ro.</p>
<p><strong>5) L&agrave; m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7841;c quan</strong>: M&#7897;t ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c s&#7921; ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p c&oacute; t&#432; duy t&iacute;ch c&#7921;c v&agrave; l&#7841;c quan cho nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; h&#7885; &#273;&#7843;m nh&#7853;n. N&#7871;u h&#7879; th&#7889;ng g&#7863;p v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; th&igrave; h&#7885; s&#7869; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch v&agrave; t&#432; v&#7845;n l&agrave;m th&#7871; n&agrave;o h&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917;a ch&#7919;a v&#7899;i c&aacute;c gi&#7843;i ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871; kh&aacute;c nhau. H&#7885; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch l&agrave;m sao &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u m&#7897;t c&aacute;ch hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;, v&agrave; t&#7841;o ra cho m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i trong d&#7921; &aacute;n m&#7897;t ni&#7873;m tin &#273;&#7875; v&#432;&#7907;t qua nh&#7919;ng th&aacute;ch th&#7913;c trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m. M&#7897;t ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c s&#432; ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m th&#7853;t s&#7921; c&#7847;n khi d&#7921; &aacute;n g&#7863;p v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; v&#7873; thi&#7871;t k&#7871; m&agrave; &#273;&#7897;i d&#7921; &aacute;n kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; c&#7913;u v&atilde;n v&agrave; h&#7885; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;a ra c&aacute;c gi&#7843;i ph&aacute;p thay th&#7871;.</p>
<p>&#272;&#7875; tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh m&#7897;t ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c s&#432; ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p &#273;&ograve;i h&#7887;i b&#7841;n h&#7885;c kh&ocirc;ng ng&#7915;ng ngh&#7881;, hi&#7875;u r&otilde; v&#7873; k&#7929; thu&#7853;t&nbsp;ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch &amp; thi&#7871;t k&#7871; ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m, c&#7853;p nh&#7853;t xu th&#7871; c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879;, tham gia th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n thi&#7871;t k&#7871; c&aacute;c h&#7879; th&#7889;ng l&#7899;n nh&#7887; v&agrave; h&#7885;c nh&#7919;ng k&#7929; n&#259;ng m&#7873;m kh&aacute;c nh&#432; giao ti&#7871;p, l&atilde;nh &#273;&#7841;o v&agrave; truy&#7873;n c&#7843;m h&#7913;ng,&hellip; nh&#432;ng ngh&#7873; ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c s&#432; ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m lu&ocirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#259;n &#273;&oacute;n.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em>Tu&#7923; Phong &ndash; APEX Global Corporation</em></span></p></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";s:7:"Hieu Le";s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";N;}s:4:"date";s:19:"2016-10-26 03:00:40";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}}i:6;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:102:"Series bảo mật nhập môn – Lưu trữ cookie – tưởng hại ai ngờ hại không tưởng";s:4:"link";s:95:"http://techtalk.vn/series-bao-mat-nhap-mon-luu-tru-cookie-tuong-hai-ai-ngo-hai-khong-tuong.html";s:11:"description";s:600:"<div>Cookie l&agrave; m&#7897;t kh&aacute;i ni&#7879;m h&#7871;t s&#7913;c c&#417; b&#7843;n m&agrave; ta &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&#7885;c khi m&#7899;i l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh web. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, n&#7871;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&uacute;ng c&aacute;ch, n&oacute; s&#7869; th&agrave;nh &ldquo;m&#7891;i ngon&rdquo; cho v&ocirc; s&#7889; hacker. B&agrave;i vi&#7871;t n&agrave;y s&#7869; &#273;&#7873; c&#7853;p &#273;&#7871;n nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;ch hacker m&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; l&#7907;i d&#7909;ng cookie &#273;&#7875; chi&#7871;m quy&#7873;n ng&#432;&#7901;i [&hellip;]</div>";s:7:"content";s:11734:"<div><p class="p1"><em><strong><span class="s1">Cookie l&agrave; m&#7897;t kh&aacute;i ni&#7879;m h&#7871;t s&#7913;c c&#417; b&#7843;n m&agrave; ta &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&#7885;c khi m&#7899;i l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh web. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, n&#7871;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&uacute;ng c&aacute;ch, n&oacute; s&#7869; th&agrave;nh &ldquo;m&#7891;i ngon&rdquo; cho v&ocirc; s&#7889; hacker.</span></strong></em></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">B&agrave;i vi&#7871;t n&agrave;y s&#7869; &#273;&#7873; c&#7853;p &#273;&#7871;n nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;ch hacker m&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; l&#7907;i d&#7909;ng cookie &#273;&#7875; chi&#7871;m quy&#7873;n ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng, t&#7845;n c&ocirc;ng h&#7879; th&#7889;ng, c&ugrave;ng v&#7899;i ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p s&#7917; d&#7909;ng cookie &#273;&uacute;ng c&aacute;ch &#273;&#7875; ng&#259;n ch&#7863;n nh&#7919;ng l&#7895; h&#7893;ng n&agrave;y nh&eacute;.</span></p>
<p class="p3"><span class="s1">Cookie &ndash; Chi&#7871;c &ldquo;b&aacute;nh qui&rdquo; v&ocirc; h&#7841;i?</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Server v&agrave; client giao ti&#7871;p v&#7899;i nhau th&ocirc;ng qua <a href="https://toidicodedao.com/2016/10/04/bao-mat-cua-giao-thuc-http/"><span class="s2">giao th&#7913;c HTTP</span></a>. &#272;&#7863;c &#273;i&#7875;m c&#7911;a giao th&#7913;c n&agrave;y l&agrave; stateless. Server kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; bi&#7871;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c 2 request c&oacute; t&#7899;i t&#7915; c&ugrave;ng 1 client hay kh&ocirc;ng.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">V&igrave; &#273;&#7863;t &#273;i&#7875;m n&agrave;y, cookie ra &#273;&#7901;i. V&#7873; b&#7843;n ch&#7845;t, cookie l&agrave; m&#7897;t file text nh&#7887; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c server g&#7917;i v&#7873; client, sau &#273;&oacute; browser l&#432;u v&agrave;o m&aacute;y ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng. Khi client g&#7917;i request t&#7899;i server, <b>n&oacute; s&#7869; g&#7917;i k&egrave;m cookie</b>. Server d&#7921;a v&agrave;o cookie n&agrave;y &#273;&#7875; nh&#7853;n ra ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Cookie th&#432;&#7901;ng c&oacute; name, value, domain v&agrave; expiration:</span></p>
<ul class="ul1"><li class="li1"><span class="s1">Name, &#273;i k&egrave;m v&#7899;i value: T&ecirc;n cookie v&agrave; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; c&#7911;a cookie &#273;&oacute;</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">Domain: Domain m&agrave; cookie &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7917;i l&ecirc;n. Nh&#432; &#7903; h&igrave;nh d&#432;&#7899;i, cookies ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7917;i khi client truy c&#7853;p wordpress.com.</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">Expiration: Th&#7901;i gian cookie t&#7891;n t&#7841;i &#7903; m&aacute;y client. Qu&aacute; th&#7901;i gian n&agrave;y, cookie s&#7869; b&#7883; xo&aacute;.</span></li>
</ul><p class="p3"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-11045" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/screen-shot-2016-10-08-at-6-08-24-pm.png" alt="screen-shot-2016-10-08-at-6-08-24-pm" width="474" height="258" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/screen-shot-2016-10-08-at-6-08-24-pm.png 474w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/screen-shot-2016-10-08-at-6-08-24-pm-300x163.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 474px) 100vw, 474px"></p>
<p class="p3"><span class="s1">B&aacute;nh qui nho nh&#7887;, &#273;&#7847;y nh&#7919;ng l&#7895; to to</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Sau khi t&igrave;m hi&#7875;u c&#417; b&#7843;n v&#7873; cookie, ta s&#7869; t&igrave;m hi&#7875;u nh&#7919;ng l&#7895;i b&#7843;o m&#7853;t m&agrave; cookie c&oacute; th&#7875; g&acirc;y ra nh&eacute;.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Nh&#432; m&igrave;nh &#273;&atilde; n&oacute;i, cookie &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7917;i k&egrave;m theo m&#7895;i request l&ecirc;n server. Server d&#7921;a theo cookie &#273;&#7875; nh&#7853;n d&#7841;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng. Do &#273;&oacute;, n&#7871;u c&oacute; th&#7875; &ldquo;ch&ocirc;m cookie&rdquo; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&aacute;c, ta c&oacute; th&#7875; m&#7841;o danh ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&oacute;.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Cookie c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7883; ch&ocirc;m theo c&aacute;c con &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng sau:</span></p>
<ul class="ul1"><li class="li1"><span class="s1">Sniff cookie qua m&#7841;ng: S&#7917; d&#7909;ng 1 s&#7889; tool &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n &#273;&#7875; sniff nh&#432; Fiddler, Wireshark, ta c&oacute; th&#7875; ch&ocirc;m cookie c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng &#7903; c&ugrave;ng m&#7841;ng. Sau &#273;&oacute;, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng <b>EditThisCookie</b> &#273;&#7875; dump cookie n&agrave;y v&agrave;o tr&igrave;nh duy&#7879;t &#273;&#7875; m&#7841;o danh ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng. (Xem demo <a href="https://toidicodedao.com/2016/10/04/bao-mat-cua-giao-thuc-http/"><span class="s2">b&agrave;i HTTP</span></a>).</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">Ch&ocirc;m cookie (Cookie thief) b&#7857;ng XSS: V&#7899;i l&#7895; h&#7895;ng XSS, hacker c&oacute; th&#7875; ch&#7841;y m&atilde; &#273;&#7897;c (JavaScript) &#7903; ph&iacute;a ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng. JS c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7885;c gi&aacute; tr&#7883; t&#7915; cookie v&#7899;i h&agrave;m <i>document.cookie</i>. Hacker c&oacute; th&#7875; g&#7917;i cookie n&agrave;y t&#7899;i server c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh. Cookie n&agrave;y s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#7875; m&#7841;o danh ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng.</span></li>
</ul><ul class="ul1"><li class="li1"><span class="s1">Th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n t&#7845;n c&ocirc;ng ki&#7875;u CRSF (Cross-site request forgery). Hacker c&oacute; th&#7875; post m&#7897;t link &#7843;nh nh&#432; sau:</span></li>
</ul><p></p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">&lt;img src="http://bank.example.com/withdraw?account=bob&amp;amount=1000000&amp;for=mallory"&gt;</pre><p></p>
<p class="p8">
</p><ul class="ul1"><li class="li1"><span class="s1">Tr&igrave;nh duy&#7879;t s&#7869; t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng load link trong &#7843;nh, d&#297; nhi&ecirc;n l&agrave; <b>c&oacute; k&egrave;m theo cookie</b>. &#272;&#432;&#7901;ng link trong &#7843;nh s&#7869; &#273;&#7885;c cookie t&#7915; request, x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng, r&uacute;t s&#7841;ch ti&#7873;n m&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng h&#7873; hay bi&#7871;t. C&aacute;ch t&#7845;n c&ocirc;ng n&agrave;y c&oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u bi&#7871;n th&#7875;, m&igrave;nh s&#7869; n&oacute;i r&otilde; &#7903; b&agrave;i vi&#7871;t sau.</span></li>
</ul><h3 class="p3"><strong><span class="s1">C&aacute;ch ph&ograve;ng ch&#7889;ng</span></strong></h3>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Xin nh&#7855;c l&#7841;i l&#7847;n th&#7913; n, c&aacute;c b&#7841;n h&#7885;c c&aacute;ch t&#7845;n c&ocirc;ng Website &#273;&#7875; bi&#7871;t m&agrave; ph&ograve;ng ch&#7889;ng ch&#7913; kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#7875; &#273;i hack ph&aacute; l&agrave;ng ph&aacute; x&oacute;m nh&eacute;. N&#7871;u g&#7863;p l&#7895; h&#7893;ng b&#7843;o m&#7853;t &#7903; trang web n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c, vui l&ograve;ng g&#7917;i mail th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho admin &#273;&#7875; h&#7885; s&#7917;a ch&#7919;a ch&#7913; &#273;&#7915;ng hack r&#7891;i <a href="https://toidicodedao.com/2015/11/05/khai-truong-trang-fanpage-cua-toi-di-code-dao-mung-blog-dat-moc-100k-view/"><span class="s2">khoe Facebook</span></a> nh&eacute;.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Ph&#7847;n n&agrave;y c&#7911;a b&agrave;i vi&#7871;t s&#7869; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n c&aacute;c b&#7841;n c&aacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng cookie &#273;&uacute;ng c&aacute;ch &#273;&#7875; tr&aacute;nh nh&#7919;ng l&#7895;i b&#7843;o m&#7853;t kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&aacute;ng c&oacute;.</span></p>
<ul class="ul1"><li class="li1"><span class="s1">Nh&#7899; set <b>Expired v&agrave; Max-Age</b>: &#272;&#7875; gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i khi cookie b&#7883; tr&#7897;m, ta kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n &#273;&#7875; cookie s&#7889;ng qu&aacute; l&acirc;u. N&ecirc;n set th&#7901;i gian s&#7889;ng c&#7911;a cookie trong kho&#7843;ng 1 ng&agrave;y t&#7899;i 3 th&aacute;ng, tu&#7923; theo y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u c&#7911;a application.</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">S&#7917; d&#7909;ng Flag <b>HTTP Only</b>: Cookie c&oacute; flag n&agrave;y s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; truy c&#7853;p th&ocirc;ng qua h&agrave;m <i>document.cookie</i>. Do &#273;&oacute;, d&ugrave; web c&oacute; b&#7883; l&#7895;i XSS th&igrave; hacker kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; &#273;&aacute;nh c&#7855;p &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&oacute;.</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">S&#7917; d&#7909;ng Flag <b>Secure</b>: Cookie c&oacute; flag n&agrave;y <b>ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7917;i qua giao th&#7913;c HTTPS</b>, hacker s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; sniff &#273;&#432;&#7907;c.</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">V&igrave; cookie d&#7877; b&#7883; t&#7845;n c&ocirc;ng, tuy&#7879;t &#273;&#7889;i <b>kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7913;a nh&#7919;ng th&ocirc;ng tin quan tr&#7885;ng </b>trong cookie (M&#7853;t kh&#7849;u, s&#7889; t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n, &hellip;). N&#7871;u b&#7855;t bu&#7897;c ph&#7843;i l&#432;u th&igrave; c&#7847;n m&atilde; ho&aacute; c&#7849;n th&#7853;n.</span></li>
</ul><p class="p1"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-11046" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/photo-1438354886727-070458b3b5cf.jpg" alt="photo-1438354886727-070458b3b5cf" width="412" height="320" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/photo-1438354886727-070458b3b5cf.jpg 412w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/photo-1438354886727-070458b3b5cf-300x233.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 412px) 100vw, 412px"></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Note th&ecirc;m: N&#7871;u website c&#7911;a b&#7841;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng RESTful API, <b>&#273;&#7915;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng cookie</b> &#273;&#7875; authorize ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng m&agrave; h&atilde;y <b>d&ugrave;ng OAuth ho&#7863;c WebToken</b>. Token n&agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c v&agrave;o Header c&#7911;a m&#7895;i request n&ecirc;n s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng b&#7883; d&iacute;nh l&#7895;i CRSF nh&eacute;.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">C&aacute;c b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; t&igrave;m hi&#7875;u th&ecirc;m v&#7873; cookie v&agrave; c&aacute;c l&#7895;i b&#7843;o m&#7853;t li&ecirc;n quan &#7903; &#273;&acirc;y:</span></p>
<ul class="ul1"><li class="li10"><span class="s9"><a href="http://resources.infosecinstitute.com/securing-cookies-httponly-secure-flags/"><span class="s10">http://resources.infosecinstitute.com/securing-cookies-httponly-secure-flags/</span></a></span></li>
<li class="li10"><span class="s9"><a href="http://www.ibm.com/support/knowledgecenter/SSZLC2_7.0.0/com.ibm.commerce.admin.doc/concepts/csesmsession_mgmt.htm"><span class="s10">http://www.ibm.com/support/knowledgecenter/SSZLC2_7.0.0/com.ibm.commerce.admin.doc/concepts/csesmsession_mgmt.htm</span></a></span></li>
<li class="li10"><span class="s9"><a href="https://www.nczonline.net/blog/2009/05/05/http-cookies-explained/"><span class="s10">https://www.nczonline.net/blog/2009/05/05/http-cookies-explained/</span></a></span></li>
<li class="li10"><span class="s9"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTTP_cookie#Secure_and_HttpOnly"><span class="s10">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTTP_cookie#Secure_and_HttpOnly</span></a></span></li>
<li class="li10"><span class="s9"><a href="http://programmers.stackexchange.com/questions/298973/rest-api-security-stored-token-vs-jwt-vs-oauth"><span class="s10">http://programmers.stackexchange.com/questions/298973/rest-api-security-stored-token-vs-jwt-vs-oauth</span></a></span></li>
